title: The Real Housewives Of Beverly Hills S04E10 Catfight On The Catw
description:
Ep 10: Catfight On The Catwalk
Yolanda chides Brandi for her behavior towards Joyce, before the ladies must share the catwalk at Kyle's fashion show.

Following the tense and unpleasant dinner at SUR, Yolanda chides Brandi for her behavior toward Joyce. Joyce and Brandi must share the catwalk at Kyle's fashion show, and Kyle hopes for the best as she raises money for charity and visits with her co-star from Halloween, Jamie Lee Curtis.
